channel.title: Please Help! I cant fix it!
channel.description:
Hey, I had a good server coming along and I was almost done, I just finished the skilling area and then... It randomly stopped working. Just look...
This is when I first start my server, everything looks fine here. [img]http://img704.imageshack.us/img704/1319/help1.png[/img]
Im using Jspeced as my base, so 2 seconds after I start the server, this box comes up (server controlls) [img]http://img689.imageshack.us/img689/6301/help2.png[/img]
After that server controll thing comes up this is what the Run box looks like [img]http://img260.imageshack.us/img260/4595/help5.png[/img]
And this is when I try to log in..... (it does this on any client!) [img]http://img260.imageshack.us/img260/241/help4o.png[/img]
Last pic... This is when I compile my server, no errors! [img]http://img708.imageshack.us/img708/1933/help3.png[/img]
The server just freezes and nothing happens, the client works fine because I have tried other servers on it. I really don't get it.... I tried earasing what i put before but that didn't work, plus that was just teleports and a shop.... If someone would help I would be extremely greatful :)
